shepherd safety systems is a startup technology company devoted to protecting workers in all segments of the energy industry our patented shepherd system combines onsite gas detection equipment with remote monitoring and notification capabilities to save lives in areas where deadly hydrogen sulfide hs and other explosive gases are presentthe shepherd system was invented over a decade ago in a garage in midland texas after losing yet another colleague gary crook decided to take action to prevent future unnecessary deaths caused by hs gas with  years of experience at all levels of the oil business gary knew that standard gas detection systems have a major flaw they only warn personnel who are being exposed to gas and those workers are expected to evacuate to a safe location but hs gas can easily incapacitate a worker and prevent selfevacuation an alarm is useless if the worker is incapacitated by gas additional deaths can occur when coworkers attempt to rescue a downed worker without taking proper precautions to protect themselves from exposureto solve this problem gary invented a mobile gas detection system that sends wireless hs alarm and gps location data to onsite and offsite personnel who can monitor ongoing activities and coordinate a safe rescue for any worker who is incapacitated by exposure to hs or other hazardous gases the shepherd system catalogues all data collected from sensors creating an extensive record of exposure levels and employees responses which increases accountability and provides invaluable information for health safety and environment professionals and executivesplease visit wwwshepherdsafetycom or call us at shepherd to learn more

sulas industries has developed a groundbreaking approach to solar tracking that uses no motors gears or electronics sulas patented heliodrive technology uses the power of the sun acting on a small amount of phase change material through simple optics to actuate a single moving part to accurately and cost effectively track the suns path across the sky the large hydraulic force generated by the heliodrive can be used to rotate a collection of photovoltaic pv panels allowing them to follow the sun and increase their energy yield the heliodrive is highly scalable and has the capability to be cost effectively applied to projects ranging from a single solar panel to largescale utility level solar projects by removing the cost and reliability barriers that have traditionally inhibited the use of solar tracking and by significantly reducing upfront operating and maintenance costs the sulas heliodrive has the potential to become the industry standard for reliable costeffective solar tracking

wellsense technology uses technical expertise design excellence and innovation to deliver practical and cost effective solutions to oilfield challenges we want to extend the life of fields maximise productivity and improve industry practices leaving a beneficial legacy for future generations our awardwinning patented fiberline intervention fli technology is a fiber optic downhole data acquisition tool it is a complete intervention system and does not rely on wireline slickline or coiled tubing for deployment it places bare fiber optic lines into oil and gas wells to capture high definition real time data the entire length of the fiber acts as a sensor and delivers a complete temperature pressure or acoustic profile of the well from top to bottom simultaneously over time activefli represents our latest development with the addition of a range of discrete measurement devices these include single point temperature and pressure sensors digital calliper gauges and an hd video camera the tools are located in the fli probe to capture additional measurements as it descends downhole they complement the distributed sensing which already takes place along the length of the fiber optic lines deployed in the well by flithe fiber probe and all downhole electronics are single use and disposable being left in the well following project completion our userfriendly customer operated plug and play system combined with the disposable nature of the technology means that intervention downtime wellsite footprint personnel requirement and associated cost and risk are all negligiblefor more information on our range of products and application please visit our website or get in touch with the team

nprex is the pioneering patentpending marketplace for direct licensing in music performing rights  the first exchange of its kind in the music industry nprex enables systematic direct licensing transactions between music publishers and music labels on the one hand and music broadcasters and digital streaming services on the other  designed and built by music industry insiders specifically for the music licensing industry with its best interests at heart nprex resolves the central questions that have confounded the music industry for decades  namely the problem of how to value a music license and the problem of how to enable the many rights holders and the many music broadcasters to coordinate directly and efficiently  nprex also resolves the fractional licensing problem as identified by the us department of justice in a simple seamless fashion  nprex does all of this across both traditional and new media licensing sources including the socalled general licensing sources such as bars restaurants music venues and the like  the centerpiece of nprex is a proprietary equilibrium pricing model derived by the nprex founder from first principles of economics that helps each side of a transaction reach a reasonable price for a direct license  the future of the troubled performing rights industry is not its past  the future is nprex

lockr is a sports coaching platform that consolidates drills plays files and other coaching material into one convenient location all while allowing coaches to instantly connect and share directly with other coaches currently the oakland raiders university of nebraskalincoln university of oregon and southern methodist university use lockr lockr allows coaches to	create and store drills plays and files so they are easily accessible on any device	share coaching material with coaches at any level locally and nationally	track and measure the mix of drills against game stats in order to calibrate the most effective practice format	capture videos of drills that use descriptions and coaching points to help teach players	upload shared videos from the website
